metadata.name: Waiting For You
metadata.description:
"Waiting For You"

She was contemplating as she sat, their love was rare, a bond that transcended distance and time.

Pure love, no words were needed to express how they felt. No matter what happened, she knew their love would remain true. It was the one thing she could hold on to, a love that would stand the test of time.

These were the thoughts running through her mind while she sat on the floor, by the door, waiting for her lover to arrive!
